{"tid":369020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人唔明石永泰講咩","createTime":"2017-08-22T03:43:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-22T07:57:05.000Z","uid":51200,"like":33,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1cfa6e5d0f56493c6c1c7da1b76bde0d3e346b55","tid":369020,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T03:43:57.000Z","msg":"佢話因爲公民抗命，<br />\n你一開始講係無畏無懼，<br />\n所以就唔應該斟酌個刑期。<br />\n<br />\n我當時聽到已經覺得好奇怪，<br />\n咁唔通假設我因爲呢d 19罪而俾人判五年丶五十年<br />\n我都唔可以出聲屌？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n三個後生因爲非法集結呢d 罪而判over 半年已經好奇怪啦，<br />\n分分鐘撞傷人都無咁重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n律政司覆核刑期個準則又唔公開，<br />\n新聞傳言滿天飛又唔僻謠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁因爲二度檢控而入獄，<br />\n造成極大社會迴響有唔俾人講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27289c7c0a2bda2d4fc8007552bfca83b194d2ef","tid":369020,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T03:46:30.000Z","msg":"要保司法獨立，無法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10c82216552e58c211b9a707ec5fcab9bfd2e3ef","tid":369020,"uid":28195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T03:54:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要保司法獨立，無法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即係咁，佢一句求仁得仁，將社運人仕等同其他罪犯，如走私運毒，出得黎行預左要還<br />\n<br />\n亦係中共要俾香港人既信息，已經畫出腸"},{"pid":"99d2a099f614244356dfcedc5291b10fef199e42","tid":369020,"uid":53687,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T03:59:13.000Z","msg":"你見啲官/特權人士幾何同市民辯論，因為佢知自己實會出醜。"},{"pid":"cd36d54f688e25e3d25e186f5824ba3205294a25","tid":369020,"uid":57705,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T04:06:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6e2741d158ac8a2815de8f750db2541c97fe35ee","tid":369020,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T04:21:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fefb45315ee9bbf9dac3e63d107877f408f61bc2","tid":369020,"uid":44358,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T04:28:36.000Z","msg":"同樣問題，問佢劉曉波坐監係咪求仁得仁，睇下佢點答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a867789299457f3b1d24c83fe23eea9e827f4acc","tid":369020,"uid":61271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T04:31:08.000Z","msg":"法律界學者係咁天真<br />\n佢地個mindset係咁樣<br />\n就算戴妖都係"},{"pid":"1ddd3d7ce26a3b6636c5b3a8383f5bbf970d8eea","tid":369020,"uid":28195,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T04:35:53.000Z","msg":"石永泰的辦公室放有英超聯球隊阿仙奴的球衣。石永泰透露，他與羅冠聰都是阿仙奴的球迷，他對羅說：「希望你出來後見到我們的愛隊捧盃。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://premium.mingpao.com/protected/Image/20170821/_21GA002_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpremium.mingpao.com%2Fprotected%2FImage%2F20170821%2F_21GA002_.jpg&h=dbe72b85&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"48b5b51401de8c1f6e70b46f650750afdee62a3c","tid":369020,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T04:39:12.000Z","msg":"係人都睇到係政治檢控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/asset